CHAT.comment: Freeplay. Mother and Child sit on living+room floor playing with a box of experimenter provided toys. They play with a miniature park which has a merry-go-round and a slide. Child does not say very much. What he does say is not very intelligible.

u.a: puts small person on plastic truck .
makes toy person go down slide .
next few utterances in high , pretending voice .
takes merry+go+round apart and looks at it .
starts putting park back in container .
puts base of merry+go+round on the floor and points to top .
